          <tr><td class="field-name">Statistic Type</td><td><span class="field-value">Reporter</span></td><td class="field-why">Groups the bar chart by who raised each issue — so you see per-member counts</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="field-name">Show Resolved</td><td><span class="field-value">Yes</span></td><td class="field-why">Includes issues that are already done — gives a complete picture, not just open ones</td></tr>
          <tr><td class="field-name">Sort By</td><td><span class="field-value">Total descending</span></td><td class="field-why">The team member who raised the most issues appears at the top</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

